    "title": "Opening for Production Engineer at Prince Pipes",
    "description": "Prince Pipes has an exciting opening for a Production Engineer at our Noida office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Prince Pipes:\nPrince Pipes is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Prince Pipes!",
